				Ok for all you shape shiftin druids listen up this is ganna help you out. Ok yes there is a way to get into the house using treeform. When you go into the little compund area with the hermits house there go all the way around to the other side. Get as close to the wall as you can and cast treeform. After you turn into a tree push into the wall, you wont go anywhere you are still a tree, while pushing in towards the building click on the treeform icon you will be forced into the house. I did this with a druid friend because you cant kite him in there you have to root him. <BR>
