				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Geez, are you really not able to scroll through five pages of info to see it's already posted how to get him out?<BR>
Now some useful information:<BR>
I did the quest once, at level 7. I spoke to the Vhalen Nostrol (sp?) guy about his tune, till he told me the hermit had the sheets. Then I walked up to the hermit's house and asked the campers there if I could loot it's corpse. The hermit had the Winds of Karana sheet 1 and the cracked lute. The lute must be given to Cordellia (or something like that) Minster, a female npc standing at one of the four wizard spires in NK. Give her the lute and get Winds of Karana sheet 2. Then head back to Vhalen and give him both the sheets. <BR>
At level 7 my reward was the FIRST bard song, chant of battle.<BR>
This song could either be random, OR based on level...so if anyone could please tell if they received different songs (one person already did, and got the Hymm of Restoration all times). <BR>
